{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775871185987,"sessionID":"ses_285d4defaffe6DUSOvUo0HSAee","part":{"id":"prt_d7a2bcf80001D3oSiOo1xM1P4N","messageID":"msg_d7a2bb54a001tV33Ld70FP15Y2","sessionID":"ses_285d4defaffe6DUSOvUo0HSAee","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:12","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/tests.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/tests.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-015: PicoD 命令执行 API - Test Specification\n2: \n3: ## Test Categories\n4: \n5: ### Unit Tests\n6: \n7: #### executor_test.go\n8: \n9: ```go\n10: // TestExecute_Success - Basic successful execution\n11: // TestExecute_Timeout - Execution timeout handling\n12: // TestExecute_ResourceLimit - Resource limit enforcement\n13: // TestExecute_InvalidCommand - Invalid command handling\n14: // TestExecute_SandboxError - Sandbox failure handling\n15: \n16: // TestExecuteAsync_Success - Basic async execution\n17: // TestExecuteAsync_QueueFull - Queue capacity handling\n18: // TestExecuteAsync_Cancellation - Async execution cancellation\n19: \n20: // TestGetStatus_Pending - Status retrieval for pending\n21: // TestGetStatus_Running - Status retrieval for running\n22: // TestGetStatus_Completed - Status retrieval for completed\n23: // TestGetStatus_NotFound - Non-existent execution\n24: \n25: // TestCancel_Running - Cancel running execution\n26: // TestCancel_Completed - Cancel already completed\n27: // TestCancel_NotFound - Cancel non-existent\n28: \n29: // TestStreamOutput_RealTime - Output streaming\n30: // TestStreamOutput_LargeOutput - Large output handling\n31: // TestStreamOutput_Closed - Stream closure handling\n32: ```\n33: \n34: ### Integration Tests\n35: \n36: #### executor_integration_test.go\n37: \n38: ```go\n39: // TestIntegration_EndToEnd - Full execution flow\n40: // TestIntegration_ConcurrentExecutions - Multiple parallel executions\n41: // TestIntegration_ResourceContention - Resource limit scenarios\n42: // TestIntegration_StatusPersistence - Status storage/retrieval\n43: // TestIntegration_CancellationRace - Race condition handling\n44: ```\n45: \n46: ### Mock Implementations\n47: \n48: ```go\n49: // MockSandboxClient - Mock sandbox for testing\n50: // MockStatusStore - Mock status storage\n51: // MockResourceLimiter - Mock resource limiting\n52: ```\n53: \n54: ## Test Data\n55: \n56: ### Sample Commands\n57: \n58: ```go\n59: var testCommands = []struct {\n60:     name    string\n61:     command string\n62:     args    []string\n63:     wantErr bool\n64: }{\n65:     {\"echo\", \"echo\", []string{\"hello\"}, false},\n66:     {\"exit_0\", \"true\", nil, false},\n67:     {\"exit_1\", \"false\", nil, true},\n68:     {\"sleep\", \"sleep\", []string{\"0.1\"}, false},\n69:     {\"invalid\", \"__invalid_command__\", nil, true},\n70: }\n71: ```\n72: \n73: ### Resource Limit Test Cases\n74: \n75: ```go\n76: var resourceTests = []struct {\n77:     name      string\n78:     memory    int64\n79:     cpu       float64\n80:     wantLimit bool\n81: }{\n82:     {\"within_limits\", 1024 * 1024 * 100, 50.0, false},\n83:     {\"exceed_memory\", 1024 * 1024 * 1024, 50.0, true},\n84:     {\"exceed_cpu\", 1024 * 1024 * 100, 150.0, true},\n85: }\n86: ```\n87: \n88: ## Coverage Targets\n89: \n90: - Line coverage: >= 85%\n91: - Branch coverage: >= 80%\n92: - Critical paths: 100%\n93: \n94: ## Test Environment\n95: \n96: - Go 1.21+\n97: - Mock sandbox implementation\n98: - In-memory status store for unit tests\n99: - Docker-based sandbox for integration tests\n100: \n101: ## Test Execution\n102: \n103: ```bash\n104: # Unit tests only\n105: go test ./pkg/picod/... -short\n106: \n107: # All tests including integration\n108: go test ./pkg/picod/...\n109: \n110: # With coverage\n111: go test ./pkg/picod/... -coverprofile=coverage.out\n112: go tool cover -html=coverage.out\n113: ```\n\n(End of file - total 113 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-015: PicoD 命令执行 API - Test Specification\n\n## Test Categories\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n#### executor_test.go\n\n```go\n// TestExecute_Success - Basic successful execution\n// TestExecute_Timeout - Execution timeout handling\n// TestExecute_ResourceLimit - Resource limit enforcement\n// TestExecute_InvalidCommand - Invalid command handling\n// TestExecute_SandboxError - Sandbox failure handling\n\n// TestExecuteAsync_Success - Basic async execution\n// TestExecuteAsync_QueueFull - Queue capacity handling\n// TestExecuteAsync_Cancellation - Async execution cancellation\n\n// TestGetStatus_Pending - Status retrieval for pending","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-015/tests.md","time":{"start":1775871185970,"end":1775871185984}}}}
